  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.2.9">
<l>ūṉē rākkaitaṉṉai yuḻantōmpi vaittamaiyāl</l>
<l>yāṉā yeṉṟaṉakkā yaṭiyēṉma ṉampukunta</l>
<l>tēṉē tīṅkarumpiṉ teḷivēyeṉ cintaitaṉṉāl</l>
<l>nāṉē yeyta<supplied>p</supplied>peṟṟēṉ naṟaiyūrniṉ ṟanampīyō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Nectar who entered the mind of me, [your] servant, as me,</l>
<l rend="indent">and for the sake of me,</l>
<l>By guarding, laboring, and caring for this body, [its] flesh soft,</l>
<l>I got to reach [you] with my thoughts,</l>
<l>Essence of sweet sugarcane, O noble who stands in Naṟaiyūr.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
